{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"629","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"四產業面臨無薪假危機 勞動部：員工進修可領時薪補助","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-02-04 18:53 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>記者林于蘅／即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87.JPG' style='width: 750px; height: 754px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>無薪假最新統計，實施人數大減<span lang='EN-US'>2133</span>人。記者葉信菉／攝影</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>武漢肺炎疫情延燒，觀旅業者首當其衝，勞動部點名四產業包括旅遊、住宿、航空、遊覽車運輸業，最快二周後將面臨無薪假危機，勞動部指出，受景氣因素導致的無薪假，勞動部提供在職進修方案，補助員工基本時薪維持生計，最高每月可領<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>小時。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>勞動部官員指出，疫情衝擊產業主要集中在旅遊、住宿、航空、遊覽車運輸業，目前仍在忙碌處理退訂業務，研判最快二周後將面臨無薪假危機。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>針對後續受到疫情衝擊業者可能放無薪假，勞動部表示，業者可申請「充電再出發訓練計畫」，勞動部將補助業者開班訓練選供進修，同時提供員工出勤可領最低薪資，保障受景氣衝擊的產業員工維持生計。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>勞動部說明，事業單位如受景氣影響須減產、停工甚至關廠，為避免大量解僱勞工，經勞資協議而達成減少工時的「無薪休假」，勞動部將挪用就業安定基金，補助業者經費開課供員工在職進修；勞動部並強調，該方案去年工具機業者也有申請，並非因應疫情而設立的紓困政策。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>除補助業者訓練費用，勞動部指出，員工在無薪假期間可領公司應發放的最低基本月薪，出勤進修課程也可領勞動部補助的基本時薪，每人每月最高可領<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>小時，也就是無薪假員工至少可領<span lang='EN-US'>23,800</span>元再加上<span lang='EN-US'>15,800</span>元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/7238/4321654</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-10","clk_count":"89"}},"__N_SSG":true}